Class SystemOwner

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Agent, MessageCommunicator

    public class SystemOwner
extends AbstractAgent
    Represents a system owner. This is a top-level agent which is used as an owner by the SystemAgentLoader, i.e. all agents created by the SystemAgentLoader have this SystemOwner instance as the owner.
